      Start of Main Content Resources


   Directory of ERIC Resource Collections -- Lists more than 900
   organizations that provide individuals with access to the ERIC database
   and related resources. It is designed to help users quickly locate
   organizations that offer ERIC resources and related services within a
   geographically short distance.
   Education Resource Organizations Directory -- Identifies organizations
   that provide information and assistance on a broad range of
   education-related topics. Continually updated and expanded, EROD
   includes information on more than 4,000 national, regional, and state
   organizations.
   ERIC Calendar of Education-Related Conferences -- Includes
   international, national, regional, and state conferences scheduled for
   this year and next year. The Calendar can be searched by keyword;
   sponsor; and conference name, date, and location.
   ERIC Electronic Mailing Lists -- Lists more than 20 listservs that are
   hosted by the ERIC system.
   Source Journal Database (CIJE) -- Contains the names, ISSN numbers, and
   subscription information for 980 major educational and
   education-related journals.
   Special Projects -- Describes the ERIC system's current
   Internet-related projects.

